        {
            "title": "Neckarinsel e.V.",
            "text": "With our research project on the water quality of the Neckar, we set out to find out when it is possible to swim in the Neckar and what conditions need to be met for this. To this end, we have been collecting various data from and in the river since 2024 and have the water quality analysed regularly by a laboratory.\n\nNeckarinsel e.V. is an association whose aim is to play an active role in shaping the future of a liveable city by the river. Stuttgart is not yet making full use of the Neckar’s potential as a recreational space and ecosystem. Through our projects and initiatives, we invite everyone to rediscover the river and become part of this transformation.\n\nWould you like to find out more about our projects?",
            "link": {
                "label": "Neckarinsel.eu",
                "url": "https://neckarinsel.eu"
